text: Looking to hone your macarons skills or simply attending a workshop with your loved ones? Look no further! Chef Roszilah is patient, knowledgeable and bubbly which made the workshop much more meaningful, interesting and lively! Highly recommended!

Finally fulfilled my dream of baking macarons! Thank you chef Rosz for the great lesson this morning! It was really well taught (: chef Rosz is a sweet and patient lady who has a great vast of knowledge in pastry baking and is willing to impart them to those who wish to learn! The new studio is nicely decorated and very cozy to be in. Great experience for me, will definitely recommend to others!  Thank you!!
Super delicious cakes and mooncakes. Beautiful batik cakes. A treat for all. Always the best from Heiraz.
